{"tid":714381,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【改詞】挑陳詠謙機！ 原曲：漸漸 陳奕迅","createTime":"2018-06-23T16:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T08:52:38.000Z","uid":172682,"like":36,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"deb008b0bc7bd806ea79985fb61c2c5766ee25e0","tid":714381,"uid":172682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:04:28.000Z","msg":"見到陳奕迅首新歌明明所有野都好正，偏偏搵咗陳詠謙填詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁就嘥咗首好歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左證明陳生有幾廢，小弟第一次寫詞，一日貨仔睇吓同佢差幾遠！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.joox.com/hk/zh_hk/single/MF+CUDKr5VokvPSlhTKf0w==?channel=SEM&amp;campaign=c_1046459510_54220154387_kwd-412631827825_262027158614_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.joox.com%2Fhk%2Fzh_hk%2Fsingle%2FMF%2BCUDKr5VokvPSlhTKf0w%3D%3D%3Fchannel%3DSEM%26campaign%3Dc_1046459510_54220154387_kwd-412631827825_262027158614_&d=OuNlpYgwBgSz3corLuT4lf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4e048732\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.joox.com/hk/zh_hk/single/MF+CUDKr5VokvPSlhTKf0w==?channel=SEM&amp;campaign=c_1046459510_54220154387_kwd-412631827825_262027158614_</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>靜夜思 原曲：漸漸 陳奕迅</strong></ins><br />\n夜靜裡 最傷神 <br />\n前塵舊愛腦內浮沉<br />\n夜幕裡那激烈擁吻<br />\n曾確信可一生抱緊<br />\n<br />\n現實令你我都走遠<br />\n情人沒法再續前緣<br />\n剩下我和月兒獨醉<br />\n難進睡 誰有罪 還潑我冷水<br />\n<br />\n剩下我日子不知怎麼過<br />\n過去的記憶褪掉可以麼<br />\n順著我們的軌跡竟走錯<br />\n錯到使 註定那情人 撇下我<br />\n<br />\n混沌過 再醒來<br />\n重頭習慣溫馨不再<br />\n用力過 與生活比賽<br />\n還確信 鮮花終會開<br />\n<br />\n慢慢我 再放膽戀愛<br />\n抬頭望向壯麗未來<br />\n但夜裡 望月兒在照<br />\n才發現 仍掛念 懷抱那撒嬌<br />\n<br />\n剩下我日子不知怎麼過<br />\n過去的記憶褪掉可以麼<br />\n順著我們的軌跡竟走錯<br />\n錯到使 註定那情人 撇下我<br />\n<br />\n命運 命運 註定愛戀短暫<br />\n舊伴卻在心底不散<br />\n彌留舊片段循環播<br />\n如被捆綁心滿痛楚<br />\n<br />\n剩下我餘生不知該怎過<br />\n我困於泥沼裡彷似經已著了魔<br />\n自問女伴只需一個 <br />\n求上天體恤我 讓我這生安穩度過"},{"pid":"3068a0fb19ee991925df78d9073df9fdb01e4854","tid":714381,"uid":172682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6850494910c23eff4cc7825ddbafd96eee076e32","tid":714381,"uid":40429,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"淨係第一段啲分句就已經唔夠陳詠謙分得準，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e0de0646b8065cc2f6173e1977ce34ce89bf22","tid":714381,"uid":136763,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"太流於情情塔塔"},{"pid":"59e50dc0edda9a32c7ee31a4300c789b7feed61f","tid":714381,"uid":41326,"like":33,"dislike":29,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:06:47.000Z","msg":"其實謙爺真係無大家所想咁唔掂"},{"pid":"4560ad94a188e1346bdcd20e432bbde41d6c710a","tid":714381,"uid":137725,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:08:24.000Z","msg":"陳詠謙 大J 笑波子"},{"pid":"ba4007bd68fe6cc038c4ff24745fd3ef21c698d2","tid":714381,"uid":39666,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:13:01.000Z","msg":"老實說，比陳詠謙更蒼白乏味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab712f5651a93c1f8a4270edf19aa970b3aba09","tid":714381,"uid":171509,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:36:25.000Z","msg":"一個字 俗"},{"pid":"abfa379d623f0a0fe8d286a1532f802f16d272db","tid":714381,"uid":148783,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:38:22.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒 你改得唔係差 <br />\n如果係Pop歌情情塌塌都無咩問題 都叫易入口 感覺上好似係幫Dear Jane改詞咁 <br />\n不過你呢個都係手詞最大既問題 你表達到既野實在係無乜特色 同不許你注定一人嗰種咁 所以我覺得有啲累贅 而漸漸呢首歌既melody唔似呢啲入口歌既melody咁快覺得好聽<br />\n所以陳詠謙作既更適合陳奕迅去唱 加上eason講故事 件事會更耐人尋味 而陳奕迅既歌好多時最後都會帶到個意義比人 會襟聽好多<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0dc9d174f08a36bd83f75a3abf5e738b19893e","tid":714381,"uid":129704,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:40:25.000Z","msg":"樓主係陳詠謙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0661aba31501a951693179be879241f4718cbb6d","tid":714381,"uid":33604,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"俗，完全唔及原著<br />\n態度仲要咁囂<br />\n柒上加柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf58bfc75f509a6dc2195bf0c7ae6f7f5005764e","tid":714381,"uid":140738,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"第一句有啲老套<br />\n<br />\n整體而言個愛情觀太幼稚<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅都四張幾<br />\n<br />\n男人老狗就算失戀都好少會咁自憐自怨啦<br />\n<br />\n就算會都收收埋埋啦"},{"pid":"ad33514c6578d5785a0782d4e6fd0cc246603049","tid":714381,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:19:36.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d65e084bf6010659b0c7ee8c390997bbf177d5d","tid":714381,"uid":4083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"未聽過首歌<br />\n齋睇 睇到打冷震<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6157abcee3c00d7d3c7b8bb7b1ad9d9adbf6a62f","tid":714381,"uid":9479,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"59e50dc0edda9a32c7ee31a4300c789b7feed61f","tid":714381,"uid":41326,"like":33,"dislike":29,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T17:06:47.000Z","msg":"其實謙爺真係無大家所想咁唔掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:35:29.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你，你d詞仲好過佢，你話掂唔掂"},{"pid":"37936ef9adee3773dabdfbaf289bef96762e06fd","tid":714381,"uid":67389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/mushrooom/2ec6ed7565248070d68b2de62df9e1d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fmushrooom%2F2ec6ed7565248070d68b2de62df9e1d2.jpg&h=0515ceb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2151583033f937a6ab9a4e08735b7d532b2cc1e2","tid":714381,"uid":42402,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"